creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Christmas in Poetry - Carols and Poems by Various.
Read in English by Greg Giordano; Sonia; Sandra Schmit; Cameron Strickland; LisaRubio; Garth Burton; Ian King
This is a volume of Christmas poems and carols, by various authors and from various times. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
